document_data.History:
When the [[Spellplague]] hit in [[1385 DR]], the western half of the Great Rift collapsed into the Underdark, forming an enormous canyon called the [[Underchasm]]. What remained of the Great Rift became known as [[East Rift]]. Underhome was destroyed in the cataclysm and the capital was moved to Eartheart.

During the [[Second Sundering]] in [[1486 DR]]. the quest of the four chosen ([[Kleef Kenric]], [[Malik el Sami]], [[Joelle Emmeline]] and [[Arietta Seasilver]]) to deliver the [[Eye of Gruumsh (relic)|''Eye of Gruumsh'']] to [[Grumbar]] for [[Luthic]] and to stop [[Shar]] restored the canyon to its former earthly land before the Spellplague.
